<p class="fn_list1"><span class="bold"><a href="#fn-11" id="fn_11">11</a></span>&#xA0;&#xA0;<span class="italic">See e.g.</span>, Martha Neil, <span class="italic">Lawyer with Little Experience Can&#x2019;t Withdraw at 11th Hour from Death-Penalty Defense, Judge Says</span>, A.B.A. Journal (May 9, 2013).</p>
